WEBVTT

00:00:04.333 --> 00:00:05.466
So it's you.

00:00:06.200 --> 00:00:08.433
Tham Hao, you beast.

00:00:08.566 --> 00:00:10.600
I regret taking you in.

00:00:10.600 --> 00:00:12.166
It's not that you look down on me.

00:00:12.166 --> 00:00:13.866
The one who looks down on you is you.

00:00:13.866 --> 00:00:15.400
You are less evasive.

00:00:15.400 --> 00:00:17.733
You left it all to Tham Hien.

00:00:17.733 --> 00:00:19.266
When do you think of me?

00:00:19.266 --> 00:00:21.533
Big brother, how can you think that, grandpa?

00:00:21.833 --> 00:00:23.500
Even though you did nothing.

00:00:23.633 --> 00:00:25.433
But grandpa never abused you.

00:00:25.433 --> 00:00:26.333
Today.

00:00:26.333 --> 00:00:28.133
Grandpa gave you half of the Tham family's power.

00:00:28.133 --> 00:00:29.933
But he didn't.

00:00:36.566 --> 00:00:38.366
Grandpa, sorry.

00:00:38.366 --> 00:00:41.733
I have been looking at your veil wrongly for so many years.

00:00:41.733 --> 00:00:43.000
Please forgive me this time.

00:00:43.000 --> 00:00:44.466
Starting today

00:00:44.766 --> 00:00:46.566
You have nothing to do with the Tham family.

00:00:46.566 --> 00:00:47.733
No need my grandfather.

00:00:47.766 --> 00:00:49.233
Go away.

00:00:57.033 --> 00:00:58.133
Grandfather.

00:01:00.200 --> 00:01:01.033
Put grandpa to bed.

00:01:01.200 --> 00:01:03.100
Take him away. Bye grandpa.